(157, 1, 'The South Bank Show', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/QBT2EAFORGpvrCY2sVLbrSj8tS.jpg', 'show', 'Documentary', '2025-10-23', '17:15:00', 'Harborview Conference Room', 'Delhi', 90.00, 200, 'The South Bank Show is a television arts magazine show that was produced by ITV between 1978 and 2010. A new series began on Sky Arts from 27 May 2012. Presented by Melvyn Bragg, the show aims to bring both high art and popular culture to a mass audience.'),
(158, 1, 'The Tyra Banks Show', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/du7W8UdGmqpqUUCZdOGGZNmD6uS.jpg', 'show', 'Talk', '2025-09-21', '12:00:00', 'Harborview Conference Room', 'Surat', 100.00, 200, 'The Tyra Banks Show, also known as and shortened to Tyra or The Tyra Show, is an American talk show hosted by Tyra Banks. The last new episode aired on Friday, May 28, 2010. The show featured many special guest stars which include Mike Epps, Cheryl Tiegs, Miley Cyrus, LL Cool J, Rihanna, Michael Rapaport, and Robbi Morgan.'),
(159, 1, 'Supernatural', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/KoYWXbnYuS3b0GyQPkbuexlVK9.jpg', 'show', 'Drama, Mystery, Sci-Fi & Fantasy', '2025-08-03', '19:30:00', 'Riverside Pavilion', 'Mumbai', 100.00, 200, 'When they were boys, Sam and Dean Winchester lost their mother to a mysterious and demonic supernatural force. Subsequently, their father raised them to be soldiers. He taught them about the paranormal evil that lives in the dark corners and on the back roads of America ... and he taught them how to kill it. Now, the Winchester brothers crisscross the country in their \'67 Chevy Impala, battling every kind of supernatural threat they encounter along the way.'),
