(168, 1, 'Pebble Mill', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500None', 'show', 'Talk', '2025-12-31', '23:00:00', 'Town Hall Auditorium', 'Mumbai', 100.00, 200, 'Pebble Mill was a re-launched version of the 1970s daily chat show Pebble Mill (also known as Pebble Mill At One for a while) which aired on BBC1 in the United Kingdom. The series premiered on October 14, 1991. The show was a mixture of celebrity guests and music. Alan Titchmarsh was a presenter on the show throughout it\'s complete run. Other presenters included Judi Spiers, Gloria Hunniford and Ross King.'),
