(183, 1, 'Saturday Night Live', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/74QkM94ur8vhJiMiqaPCqkQeBYl.jpg', 'show', 'Comedy, News', '2025-08-12', '10:00:00', 'Uptown Banquet Hall', 'Mumbai', 50.00, 200, 'A late-night live television sketch comedy and variety show created by Lorne Michaels. The show\'s comedy sketches, which parody contemporary culture and politics, are performed by a large and varying cast of repertory and newer cast members. Each episode is hosted by a celebrity guest, who usually delivers an opening monologue and performs in sketches with the cast, and features performances by a musical guest.'),
